WAFER WORKS CORP June Sales Rise 32.75% (Table) : 6182 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-08T00:56:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/wafer-works-corp-june-sales-rise-32-75-table-6182-tt.html
WAFER WORKS CORP (6182)  said unconsolidated sales
in June rose 32.75% to NT$575,337,000 from NT$433,401,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            575,337          433,401    
YOY%              32.75%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           3,204,720        2,137,195   
YOY%              49.95% 
=================================================================
 